title: Coronavirus variant fear sparks Africa travel curbs
content: Six southern African countries are put on the red list, amid "deep concern" over a new variant of the virus.

title: Starmer: Over a year since I spoke to Corbyn
content: The Labour leader says it is up to his predecessor to regain the party whip before the next election.

title: PM calls on France to take back migrants
content: A returns agreement would have an "immediate" impact on the number of crossings, Boris Johnson says.

title: Women MPs lobby Speaker against babies in debates
content: Sir Lindsay Hoyle says MPs have texted "do not give in" after Labour's Stella Creasy raised the issue.

title: Highest UK asylum claims since 2004
content: Separate figures show net migration to the UK fell 88% last year due to Covid restrictions.

title: Female Dr Who robs boys of role models, claims MP
content: MP Nick Fletcher suggests boys are turning to crime because male characters tend to be criminals.

title: Improve cross-border rail and roads, review says
content: A review of UK transport links recommends improving the A1, A75, A77, and upgrading the east and west coast mainlines.
